To run a PlumeMoM & Hysplit simulation

1. Edit input_file.py 

2. Execute run_plumemom_hysplit.sh   - To run the PlumeMoM & Hysplit simulation

3. Execute create_plots.sh           - HYSPLIT plotting routines for solid particles and gas concentrations

4. Execute plot_ground_mass.sh       - To plot the deposit

5. Execute extract_samples.sh        - To extract particles mass loading at specific lat-lon locations (see input_file.py)

6. Execute calculate_solid_mass.sh   - To compute the mass of solid material in the domain 

7. Execute calculate_gas_mass.sh     - To compute the mass of volcanic gases in the domain

8. Execute clean_all.py              - To clean the working directory

From point 3 to point 8 the execution order can be varied by the user
